      "title": "3263 dengue patients",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Health has informed that 3263 dengue patients have been reported in the country in the last week as dengue fever is spreading rapidly across the country.",
        "The Ministry has informed that more dengue cases are reported in Colombo district and till now 1004 people have been affected by dengue disease, 516 people have been reported in Gampaha district, 332 people in Kalutara district, 332 people in Kandu district, 160 people in Galle district, 153 people in Ratnapura district and 154 people in Kekalai district."
      ],
